    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/872f9675f087f5c1224ba3424e105d59.avif?t=1769043337\" width=780 height=150 /></span>爱人、小马、触手、猫咪。还有一匹怒火中烧、手持枪械的小马。在《Get Your Tentacles Off My Waifu》这款游戏里，你的任务是拯救那些被触手怪纠缠的小马爱人。在这场混战中，机敏地躲避那些占有欲极强的怪物至关重要，它们可是不会轻易放手的。小心行事，别让自己成为它们的下一顿大餐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/286516fa6b346f4d2b91b5d5eaea175e.poster.avif?t=1769043337\" width=780 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/286516fa6b346f4d2b91b5d5eaea175e.webm?t=1769043337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/286516fa6b346f4d2b91b5d5eaea175e.mp4?t=1769043337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松搞定？领走你的第一位爱人，然后看看接下来会发生什么——她们不只是等你来解救的萌妹子。除非你想要调皮一下，把她们投向那些 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >触手怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可真是个捣蛋鬼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/f2322591bb52f080210f9546c4b2c250.poster.avif?t=1769043337\" width=780 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/f2322591bb52f080210f9546c4b2c250.webm?t=1769043337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/f2322591bb52f080210f9546c4b2c250.mp4?t=1769043337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/63fddd1ee2ee424ac0b099791264bd95.avif?t=1769043337\" width=780 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GYTOMW带你重温那些怀旧的射击游戏时光，它是那种一上手就能嗨起来的清版射击游戏。想要闯过第一关？不用做到像素级的完美，只要你的枪法还算靠谱，大多数时候都够用了。放心，这游戏不会在你刚碰一下就让你的游戏机变成砖头。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 一个真正的故事！万事皆有因果。这包括猫，大量的猫。当然，还有小马。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 夺回你的爱人！有19.5位小马爱人等着你从巨型触手怪的魔爪中拯救出来。救下她们后，尽情享受丰富的互动（每个选择都有其后果哦）——或者干脆把她们扔向那些怪物。你这个调皮鬼。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 丰富的非射击游戏玩法！除了探索美妙的小马爱人世界，你还可以冥想小马禅，参与必不可少的制作系统，当然，还有负责任地使用星尘。非常负责任哦。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 多重结局等你来发现！你的话语和对待爱人的方式将影响游戏的结局。你知道这意味着什么，对吧？那就是重玩价值啦！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > “等等，游戏里竟暗藏玄机？” 没错，每一处都环环相扣，没有偶然，全是精心设计。是的，这正是那种游戏。如果你愿意深挖，就会发现隐藏在表象之下的奇异深度……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/e57a15c188f3fc63df5118c6be7739b9.poster.avif?t=1769043337\" width=780 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/e57a15c188f3fc63df5118c6be7739b9.webm?t=1769043337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174750/extras/e57a15c188f3fc63df5118c6be7739b9.mp4?t=1769043337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
